# PowerEdge R720xd (gen 12, 2U dual-socket, 12-26 LFF/SFF drives).
#
# UNTESTED — same caveats as R720. Gen 12 BMC behavior varies per chassis,
# can't safely assume R730xd-style clamping. Default MIN_FAN=20 is
# conservative.
#
# Probe before lowering — see r720.env for procedure.

: "${MIN_FAN:=20}"
